/>\n得矣磚瓦<br />\n賺18400，加上拔一個牙香港可能要700、老莊自己賺取(典型的窮人思維：儉成小富！)<br />\n22200+18400+700=41300<br />\n所以老莊不明白：讀書好？麻將妙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:45:16.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698e39af57b54ac7e08c9ca5d85b225ecfb030e7","tid":1671920,"uid":244318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bb9dca1774593b75de4d2be40edb65caa24854c","tid":1671920,"uid":325346,"like":10,"dislike":55,"score":-45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T20:10:41.000Z","msg":"肯捱下苦做地盤應該無咩問題<br />\n信左主可以睇神學做牧師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n管牧師咁幫佢唔洗同佢擔心<br />\n教會俾份文職工、聖公會咁多機構俾份工唔會好難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"呢件殺人犯害撚左咁多手足 同政府一樣都係大仆街"},{"pid":"e7869d0786deb18b6b3a6e9a9d453df8b2b4f0c0","tid":1671920,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"上前線！"},{"pid":"356bf2dd30de5f7de6cef5ebfe411ae28077a1b1","tid":1671920,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"佢個人做錯既野係佢個人問題！利用佢班狗官先係始作俑者！唔好迫佢做多次政治棋子！"},{"pid":"51d8c0915e86ab2e211dbcef52a0bf95d1830617","tid":1671920,"uid":263038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:02:25.000Z","msg":"點解施君龍當年放火燒死人先坐8年<br />\n而家仲要大富大貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bc883e7908fb9850efad967971e241c301158f","tid":1671920,"uid":322578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:05:12.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1280775ba61c20a5cdf6e23d6fb2a36798b59b77","tid":1671920,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0caead0a7d734a9c9b7f7884ad3589281d30abf7","tid":1671920,"uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:01:03.000Z","msg":"脫墨代言人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"<span sty